20next%20tackle%2C%20whether%20the%20next%20play%20will%20be%20a%20run%20or%20a%20pass.%20AI%20companies%20like%20SimpleBet%20(recently%20acquired%20by%20DraftKings%20for%20%24195%20million)%20have%20automated%20processes%20that%20allow%20the%20maximum%20number%20of%20possible%20micro%20bets%20to%20increase%20by%20an%20order%20of%20magnitude.%20No%20longer%20bottlenecked%20by%20the%20capabilities%20of%20human%20sportsbook%20odds%20calculators%2C%20every%20moment%20of%20a%20sports%20game%20can%20be%20turned%20into%20a%20wager.%20Won%20your%20bet%20that%20Lamar%20Jackson%20would%20throw%20on%202nd%20and%2010%3F%20Why%20not%20bet%20again%20that%20he'll%20scramble%20for%20the%20first%20down%20on%203rd%20and%203%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPhysical%20casinos%20are%20also%20looking%20to%20harness%20AI%20for%20efficiency%20gains.%20nQube%2C%20a%20Canadian%20startup%20run%20by%20a%20physics%20professor%2C%20uses%20machine%20learning%20to%20optimize%20the%20placement%20of%20slot%20machines%20on%20casino%20floors%2C%20profiling%20players%20and%20the%20performance%20of%20one-armed%20bandits%20individually%20and%20collectively%20%E2%80%94%20replacing%20an%20older%20generation%20of%20floor-manager%20intuition%20and%20basic%20analysis.%20Some%20of%20nQube's%20findings%20have%20been%20counterintuitive%3A%20It%20turns%20out%20that%20removing%20the%20total%20number%20of%20slot%20machines%20can%20often%20increase%20the%20casino's%20%26quot%3Bwin%2C%26quot%3B%20if%20the%20machines%20are%20arranged%20in%20a%20way%20that%20redirects%20players%20to%20games%20where%20they'll%20make%20larger%20bets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJason%20Feige%2C%20a%20cofounder%20of%20nQube%2C%20had%20been%20working%20on%20computational%20astrophysics%20when%20his%20partner%2C%20Stasi%20Baran%2C%20found%20a%20scientific%20paper%20about%20the%20problem%20of%20optimal%20casino%20floor%20planning.%20Though%20neither%20had%20any%20gaming%20experience%2C%20they%20both%20realized%20their%20work%20could%20be%20a%20fit.%20%26quot%3BI%20like%20math%20and%20I%20like%20hard%20problems%2C%20and%20she%20brought%20me%20just%20a%20monster%20of%20a%20problem%20and%20I%20just%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Feige%20says.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20never%20seen%20data%20as%20clean%20and%20as%20comprehensive%20as%20what%20you%20see%20in%20this%20industry%2C%20largely%20because%20it%20is%20so%20heavily%20regulated.%20But%20that%20combined%20with%20the%20kind%20of%20powerful%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-ai-leader-artificial-superintelligence-agi-test-time-compute-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EAI%20systems%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20I've%20been%20building%2C%20it%20was%20just%20such%20a%20natural%20fit.%20I%20just%20absolutely%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20the%20industry.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20prospect%20of%20deeper%20AI%20integration%20is%20definitely%20in%20the%20air.%20At%20one%20of%20the%20gambling%20industry's%20biggest%20events%2C%20G2E%2C%20a%20glitzy%20conference%20held%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkey-sports-betting-online-gambling-trends-to-watch-g2e-recap-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ELas%20Vegas%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20September%2C%20there%20were%20packed%20panels%20on%20AI%20in%20sports%20betting%2C%20women%20in%20AI%2C%20AI-powered%20behavioral%20analytics%20and%20%26quot%3Bresponsible%20gambling%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20AI%20for%20customer%20relationships.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20enticing%2C%20and%20controversial%2C%20uses%20of%20AI%20in%20gambling%20is%20customizing%20casinos%20%E2%80%94%20virtual%20and%20on%20the%20floor%20%E2%80%94%20to%20each%20gambler.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-nfl-streaming-24-million-christmas-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ENetflix%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20uses%20machine%20learning%20and%20data%20science%20to%20tailor%20each%20user's%20feed%20to%20what%20they're%20most%20likely%20to%20binge%2C%20the%20startup%20Future%20Anthem%20uses%20similar%20tools%20to%20keep%20users%20hooked%20on%20casino%20websites.%20The%20UK-based%20software%20provider%20builds%20a%20personalized%2C%20dynamic%20homepage%2C%20presenting%20the%20exact%20right%20game%20%E2%80%94%20bingo%2C%20slots%2C%20poker%20%E2%80%94%20to%20cater%20to%20a%20player's%20desires%20at%20the%20exact%20right%20moment%2C%20offering%20bonuses%20if%20the%20player%20is%20getting%20dejected%20and%20keeping%20them%20betting%20for%20longer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20machine-learning%20models%20that%20are%20understanding%20and%20humanizing%20that%20player%2C%20that%20player%20data%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Ian%20Tibot%2C%20Future%20Anthem's%20chief%20commercial%20officer.%20%26quot%3BWe%20see%20every%20single%20spin%20of%20a%20slot%2C%20we%20see%20every%20single%20bet%2C%20and%20we%20actually%20understand%20the%20experience%20that%20the%20player%20is%20having%20by%20creating%20the%20concept%20of%20a%20session%20out%20of%20that%20data%2C%20and%20that%20allows%20us%20to%20understand%20changes%20in%20patterns%20of%20behavior.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrick-and-mortar%20casinos%20are%20also%20digitally%20profiling%20their%20users.%20Some%20locations%20have%20RFID%20chips%20embedded%20in%20every%20gambling%20chip%2C%20tracking%20how%20each%20gambler%20is%20playing%20and%20building%20a%20profile%20that%20automatically%20directs%20human%20workers%20to%20intervene%20as%20needed%20%E2%80%94%20an%20extra%20free%20drink%20here%2C%20a%20bonus%20spin%20there.%20%26quot%3BBefore%20it%20used%20to%20be%20like%20a%20pit%20boss%20maybe%20having%20their%20eyes%20on%2040%20players%20across%20five%20tables%26quot%3B%20to%20monitor%20bet%20sizes%20and%20manually%20assign%20perks%20and%20freebies%2C%20says%20Kasra%20Ghaharian%2C%20a%20researcher%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Nevada%2C%20Las%20Vegas%2C%20International%20Gaming%20Institute.%20%26quot%3BIt%20wasn't%20very%20accurate%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20AI%20allows%20casinos%20to%20%26quot%3Bbe%20much%20more%20precise%20in%20how%20you're%20tracking%20that%20activity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20using%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-transforming-technical-work-vercel-julius-developers-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EAI%20for%20efficiency%20gains%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20user%20profiling%2C%20the%20industry's%20ultimate%20vision%20for%20employing%20the%20technology%20is%20much%20more%20ambitious%20%E2%80%94%20and%20unsettling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20research%20paper%20published%20last%20May%2C%20the%20consultancy%20giant%20Deloitte's%20Global%20Lottery%20and%20Gambling%20Centre%20of%20Excellence%20predicted%20a%20future%20where%20every%20game%20could%20be%20personalized%20in%20real%20time%20to%20appeal%20to%20individual%20gamblers.%20Generative%20AI%2C%20the%20authors%20wrote%2C%20could%20%26quot%3Ballow%20the%20games%20themselves%20to%20generate%20content%20based%20on%20the%20explicit%20or%20even%20implicit%20actions%20of%20players%2C%20from%20instantly%20generated%20new%20items%20and%20playing%20levels%20to%20in-game%20characters%20that%20can%20have%20lifelike%20discussions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20technology%2C%20they%20continued%2C%20could%20create%20%26quot%3Bindividually%20themed%20online%20slot%20games%20that%20can%20respond%20to%20a%20player's%20voice%20and%20even%20generate%20novel%20content%20in%20response%20to%20a%20player's%20behavior%20and%20game%20history.%26quot%3B%20Generative%20AI%20chatbots%20the%20players%20could%20talk%20to%2C%20games%20with%20themes%20automatically%20tailored%20to%20their%20preference%20%E2%80%94%20the%20ultimate%20filter%20bubble.%20Social%20media's%20endlessly%20personalized%20carousel%20of%20content%20is%20already%20notoriously%20addictive%2C%20and%20the%20damaging%20parasocial%20relationships%20that%20can%20be%20formed%20with%20AI%20chatbots%20are%20currently%20under%20a%20microscope%20following%20reports%20of%20suicide%20and%20self-harm%20linked%20to%20a%20popular%20provider.%20Adding%20these%20elements%20to%20the%20famously%20powerful%20money-extraction%20machine%20that%20is%20online%20gambling%20is%20a%20potent%20combination.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGambling%20is%20historically%20a%20human-centric%20business%20%E2%80%94%20gamblers%20try%20their%20luck%20against%20the%20house%2C%20for%20better%20or%20worse.%20But%20Christina%20Thakor-Rankin%2C%20a%20veteran%20industry%20consultant%20based%20in%20the%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20dreams%20of%20an%20automatically%20managed%20brick-and-mortar%20casino%20in%20the%20years%20and%20decades%20ahead%2C%20akin%20to%20Amazon's%20automated%20Go%20convenience%20stores%2C%20with%20unnecessary%20human%20staff%20costs%20eating%20into%20the%20casino's%20margins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLook%20at%20the%20amount%20of%20operating%20expenditure%20required%20in%20terms%20of%20serving%20customers%2C%20monitoring%20customers%2C%20keeping%20them%20safe%2C%20people%20who%20work%20in%20the%20cage%20or%20the%20cashier%20pit%20bosses.%20What%20if%20you%20had%20a%20casino%20that%20was%20very%20similar%20to%20the%20new%20generation%20of%20self-service%20Amazon%20stores%20where%20you%20don't%20need%20cash%20and%20you%20don't%20need%20people%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20asked.%20%26quot%3BHow%20would%20that%20kind%20of%20technology%20transform%20a%20world%20of%20sportsbooks%2C%20but%20also%20land-based%20casinos%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20least%20one%20casino%20workers%20union%2C%20the%20Culinary%20Workers%20Union%2C%20has%20raised%20concerns%20about%20the%20risk%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblue-collar-job-demand-growth-white-collar-layoffs-ai-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eblue-collar%20jobs%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Las%20Vegas%20being%20automated.%20In%202019%2C%20The%20Nevada%20Independent%20reported%20that%20between%2038%25%20and%2065%25%20of%20casino%20jobs%20(depending%20on%20the%20study%20cited)%20in%20the%20south%20of%20the%20state%20could%20be%20automated%20over%20the%20next%20decade%20and%20a%20half%2C%20calling%20the%20city%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20to%20automation%20in%20the%20entire%20country.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20many%20gamblers%2C%20a%20trip%20to%20Vegas%20isn't%20just%20a%20transaction%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20an%20experience%2C%20punctuated%20by%20banter%20with%20dealers%2C%20table%20service%2C%20shows%2C%20and%20the%20seedy%20glamour%20of%20the%20strip.%20It%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20if%20they%20will%20accept%20a%20robot%20substitute.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EArtificial%20intelligence%20may%20be%20a%20moneymaker%20for%20gambling%20companies%2C%20but%20the%20companies%20say%20it's%20also%20something%20else%3A%20a%20remedy%20for%20problem%20gambling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlaytech%2C%20a%20European%20gambling%20software%20provider%2C%20is%20one%20of%20several%20firms%20using%20AI%20to%20try%20to%20suss%20out%20when%20a%20gambler%20is%20demonstrating%20signs%20of%20addiction%20or%20problematic%20play%20and%20intervene.%20Part%20of%20this%20is%20recognizing%20a%20player's%20patterns%20%E2%80%94%20larger-than-usual%20bets%2C%20or%20declined%20deposits%2C%20or%20playing%20at%20unexpected%20times%20%E2%80%94%20and%20interjecting%20with%20prompts%20suggesting%20they%20take%20a%20break.%20(Future%20Anthem%20says%20its%20systems%20can%20also%20detect%20aberrant%20behavior%20and%20automatically%20check%20in%20with%20target%20gamblers.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnline%20gambling%20companies%20have%20lots%2C%20tons%20of%20data%20about%20their%20players%20because%20every%20single%20bet%20or%20every%20spin%20on%20a%20slot%2C%20every%20single%20deposit%2C%20the%20time%20you%20spend%20online%2C%20there's%20lots%20of%20information%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Francesco%20Rodano%2C%20Playech's%20chief%20policy%20officer.%20%26quot%3BSo%20we%20train%20an%20AI%20model%20to%20analyze%20this%20behavior%20and%20recognize%20possible%20harmful%20patterns.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlaytech%20and%20other%20gambling%20companies%20are%20also%20developing%20chatbots%20that%20gamblers%20can%20talk%20to%20about%20addiction%20%E2%80%94%20the%20logic%20being%20that%20because%20gambling%20addiction%20is%20stigmatized%2C%20addicts%20may%20actually%20be%20more%20comfortable%20talking%20to%20a%20nonhuman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERodano%20acknowledges%20that%20the%20same%20technology%20that%20could%20help%20problem%20gamblers%20could%20also%20be%20used%20to%20exacerbate%20their%20addictions.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20use%20a%20tool%20like%20ours%20to%20identify%20vulnerable%20players%2C%20in%20theory%2C%20you%20could%20use%20that%20information%20to%20target%20them%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20the%20opposite%20of%20what%20the%20tool%20is%20intended%20for%2C%20which%20is%20totally%20unethical%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20operate%20in%20a%20regulated%20market%2C%20it's%20very%20unlikely%20to%20happen%20because%20the%20regulator%20would%20notice%20that%20and%20clamp%20down.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmid%20frothy%20valuations%20and%20wild%20hype%2C%20there's%20a%20risk%20of%20overstating%20the%20technology's%20near-term%20promise%20%E2%80%94%20particularly%20the%20more%20giddy%20ideas%2C%20such%20as%20Thakor-Rankin's%20predictions%20of%20a%20Caesar's%20Palace%20augmented%20with%20robotic%2C%20voice-activated%20%26quot%3BCenturions.%26quot%3B%20And%20some%20industry%20insiders%20say%20that%20what's%20now%20called%20AI%20might%20be%20considered%20statistics%20or%20big%20data%2C%20just%20rebranded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20like%20to%20say%20that%20we've%20been%20doing%20AI%20since%20before%20it%20was%20cool%20and%20this%20new%20age%20of%20AI%20hype%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20been%20very%20interesting%20to%20navigate%20because%20on%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20everyone%20wants%20to%20talk%20about%20AI%2C%20which%20is%20great%20for%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Stasi%20Baran%2C%20nQube's%20cofounder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20there's%20so%20much%20noise%20to%20sift%20through%20for%20our%20customers%20and%20for%20us%20as%20well%20to%20determine%2C%20everyone%20says%20that%20they've%20got%20an%20AI%20product%2C%20but%20what's%20actually%20real%20and%20what%20actually%20brings%20real%20value%3F%20I%20mean%2C%20that's%20difficult%20to%20determine.%20I%20think%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20overnight%20AI%20experts%20out%20there%2C%20and%20that%20concerns%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20AI%20frothiness%20isn't%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgenerative-ai-market-froth-openai-cerebras-meta-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eunique%20to%20the%20gambling%20industry%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20the%20space%20has%20long%20had%20a%20nose%20for%20innovations%20that%20boost%20its%20bottom%20line%20%E2%80%94%20from%20the%20development%20of%20electromechanical%20slot%20machines%20in%20the%201960s%20to%20the%20creation%20of%20loyalty%20programs%20for%20high%20rollers%20in%20the%20'80s.%20As%20ever%2C%20the%20house%20always%20wins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Frob-price%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3ERob%20Price%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20correspondent%20for%20Business%20Insider%20and%20writes%20features%20and%20investigations%20about%20the%20technology%20industry.%20His%20Signal%20number%20is%20%2B1%20650-636-6268%2C%20and%20his%20email%20is%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Arprice%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Erprice%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgambling-industry-ai-big-bets-casinos-desperate-americans-las-vegas-202