20joint%20venture%20with%20GIC%20of%20Singapore%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsterlite-grid-32-gets-rs-2-450-cr-via-listed-ncds-to-refinance-muml-project-125010600520_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tamil%20Nadu%20Governor's%20Walkout%20Over%20Anthem%20Row%2C%20MK%20Stalin's%20%26quot%3BChildish%26quot%3B%20Jab%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETamil%20Nadu%20Governor%20RN%20Ravi%20refused%20to%20deliver%20his%20customary%20address%20to%20the%20Assembly%20today%20and%20walked%20out%20in%20protest%20of%20the%20National%20Anthem%20not%20being%20sung%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20address.%20As%20per%20tradition%2C%20the%20state%20anthem%20Tamil%20Thai%20Valthu%20is%20sung%20when%20the%20House%20meets%20and%20the%20National%20Anthem%20at%20the%20end.%20But%20Governor%20Ravi%20has%20taken%20exception%20to%20this%20norm%20and%20said%20the%20national%20anthem%20should%20be%20sung%20at%20both%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Constitution%20of%20Bharat%20and%20the%20National%20Anthem%20were%20once%20again%20insulted%20in%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Assembly%20today.%20Respecting%20the%20National%20Anthem%20is%20among%20the%20first%20Fundamental%20Duty%20as%20enshrined%20in%20our%20Constitution.%20It%20is%20sung%20in%20all%20the%20state%20legislatures%20at%20the%20beginning%20and%20the%20end%20of%20Governor's%20address%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20after%20the%20Governor%20walked%20out%20today.%20%26quot%3BToday%20on%20arrival%20of%20Governor%20to%20the%20House%20only%20Tamil%20Thaai%20Vaazhthu%20was%20sung.%20Governor%20respectfully%20reminded%20the%20House%20of%20its%20Constitutional%20Duty%20and%20fervently%20appealed%20to%20the%20Hon'ble%20Chief%20Minister%20who%20is%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20House%20and%20the%20Hon'ble%20Speaker%20for%20singing%20the%20National%20Anthem.%20However%2C%20they%20cussedly%20refused.%20It%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20grave%20concern.%20Not%20to%20be%20a%20party%20to%20such%20brazen%20disrespect%20to%20the%20Constitution%20and%20the%20National%20Anthem%2C%20Governor%20in%20deep%20anguish%20left%20the%20House%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20MK%20Stalin%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%20that%20the%20Governor%20had%20made%20it%20a%20custom%20to%20violate%20the%20Assembly's%20tradition%20and%20called%20his%20actions%20%26quot%3Bchildish%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BAccording%20to%20the%20Constitution%2C%20it%20is%20a%20tradition%20of%20legislative%20democracy%20for%20the%20state%20governor%20to%20read%20the%20government's%20address%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20year!%20He%20has%20made%20it%20his%20custom%20to%20violate%20it%20%40rajbhavan_TN.%20It%20is%20childish%20that%20the%20governor%2C%20who%20has%20cut%20out%20what%20was%20there%20and%20added%20what%20was%20not%2C%20has%20gone%20without%20reading%20it%20this%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20passages%20skipped%20by%20the%20Governor%20in%20his%20earlier%20speeches%20in%20Assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Governor's%20actions%20in%20continuously%20insulting%20the%20people%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20the%20government%20elected%20by%20them%2C%20and%20the%20century-old%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Legislative%20Assembly%20are%20unbecoming%20of%20the%20position%20he%20holds.%20Why%20should%20someone%20who%20is%20unwilling%20to%20perform%20their%20political%20and%20legal%20duties%20remain%20in%20office%20is%20the%20question%20on%20everyone's%20mind!%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Governor%20walked%20out%2C%20Assembly%20Speaker%20M%20Appavu%20delivered%20the%20customary%20address%20that%20was%20to%20be%20read%20by%20the%20Governor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan%20and%20the%20DMK%20government%20have%20sparred%20over%20the%20custom%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20February%2C%20the%20Governor%20had%20refused%20to%20deliver%20the%20customary%20address%20to%20the%20Assembly%20and%20said%20the%20draft%20had%20%26quot%3Bnumerous%20passages%20with%20misleading%20claims%20far%20from%20truth%26quot%3B.%20The%20Raj%20Bhavan%20also%20said%20that%20the%20National%20Anthem%20must%20be%20shown%20due%20respect%20and%20played%20both%20at%20the%20beginning%20and%20end%20of%20the%20Governor's%20address.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20R%20N%20Ravi%20refused%20to%20read%20parts%20of%20the%20speech%20that%20had%20the%20names%20of%20BR%20Ambedkar%2C%20Periyar%2C%20CN%20Annadurai%20besides%20the%20phrase%20'Dravidian%20Model'%20and%20some%20references%20to%20law%20and%20order%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20He%20had%20then%20walked%20out%20even%20without%20waiting%20for%20the%20national%20anthem%20after%20the%20House%20adopted%20a%20resolution%20to%20record%20only%20the%20official%20speech%20and%20not%20the%20Governor's%20version.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEver%20since%20he%20took%20over%20as%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Governor%20in%202021%2C%20Mr%20Ravi%20has%20had%20frosty%20ties%20with%20the%20MK%20Stalin-led%20state%20government.%20The%20DMK%20government%20has%20accused%20him%20of%20acting%20like%20a%20BJP%20spokesperson%20and%20blocking%20Bills%20and%20appointments.%20The%20Governor%20has%20said%20the%20Constitution%20empowers%20him%20to%20withhold%20his%20assent%20to%20legislation.%20The%20dispute%20between%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan%20and%20state%20government%20has%20also%20reached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20Rashtrapati%20Bhavan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20Madras%20High%20Court%20have%20held%20that%20Governors%20ought%20to%20function%20on%20the%20aid%20and%20advice%20of%20the%20cabinet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736153640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2F3j6upi3g_mk-stalin-rn-ravi-stalin-ravi-ani_625x300_30_Jun