0has%20been%20accused%20of%20using%20allegations%20against%20India%20to%20deflect%20attention%20from%20mounting%20domestic%20challenges%2C%20including%20a%20falling%20economy%2C%20and%20dissent%20within%20his%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELiberal%20Party%20Rebellion%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20year%2C%20several%20high-profile%20Liberal%20Party%20MPs%2C%20including%20Sean%20Casey%20and%20Ken%20McDonald%2C%20have%20publicly%20called%20for%20Trudeau%20to%20step%20down%2C%20citing%20dissatisfaction%20with%20his%20leadership.%20Reports%20suggest%20that%20more%20than%2020%20Liberal%20MPs%20have%20signed%20a%20pledge%20demanding%20his%20resignation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20resignation%20of%20Chrystia%20Freeland%20as%20Deputy%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20Finance%20Minister%20in%20December%20marked%20a%20blow%20to%20Trudeau's%20government.%20Freeland's%20departure%20reportedly%20stemmed%20from%20policy%20disagreements%2C%20including%20Trudeau's%20handling%20of%20potential%20US%20tariffs%20and%20his%20economic%20strategy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLike%20most%20families%2C%20sometimes%20we%20have%20fights%20around%20the%20holidays%2C%26quot%3B%20Trudeau%20said%20in%20December.%20%26quot%3BBut%20of%20course%2C%20like%20most%20families%2C%20we%20find%20our%20way%20through%20it.%20You%20know%2C%20I%20love%20this%20country%2C%20I%20deeply%20love%20this%20party%2C%20I%20love%20you%20guys%2C%20and%20love%20is%20what%20families%20are%20all%20about.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFreeland%2C%20who%20slammed%20Trudeau%20and%20his%20%26quot%3Bcostly%20political%20gimmicks%26quot%3B%20in%20her%20resignation%20letter%2C%20did%20not%20share%20that%20sentiment.%20Following%20Freeland's%20resignation%2C%20Trudeau%20largely%20disappeared%20from%20media%20briefings%20or%20public%20events%20while%20spending%20much%20of%20his%20time%20at%20a%20ski%20resort.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdding%20to%20the%20internal%20turmoil%2C%20the%20Liberal%20Party%20suffered%20losses%20in%20two%20recent%20by-elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKey%20allies%20like%20New%20Democratic%20Party%20(NDP)%20leader%20Jagmeet%20Singh%20have%20said%20that%20he%20would%20introduce%20a%20motion%20in%20the%20Canadian%20Parliament%20to%20topple%20the%20government.%20Currently%20on%20Winter%20Break%2C%20the%20Canadian%20Parliament%20will%20resume%20its%20proceedings%20on%20January%2027.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELeadership%20Scenarios%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Trudeau%20resigns%2C%20the%20Liberal%20Party's%20main%20challenge%20would%20be%20to%20find%20a%20leader%20with%20mass%20appeal.%20In%20Canada%2C%20an%20interim%20leader%20cannot%20run%20for%20the%20party's%20permanent%20leadership.%20Names%20like%20Dominic%20LeBlanc%2C%20Melanie%20Joly%2C%20Francois-Philippe%20Champagne%2C%20and%20Mark%20Carney%20have%20been%20floated%20as%20potential%20contenders%2C%20but%20the%20timeline%20for%20a%20leadership%20race%20could%20leave%20the%20party%20vulnerable%20in%20the%20lead-up%20to%20the%20federal%20elections%20scheduled%20later%20this%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECanada's%20Liberal%20leader%20is%20chosen%20through%20a%20special%20convention%2C%20a%20process%20that%20could%20take%20months.%20If%20an%20election%20were%20called%20before%20the%20Liberals%20have%20a%20permanent%20leader%2C%20the%20party%20would%20face%20risks%20at%20the%20ballot%20box.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrudeau's%20political%20troubles%20come%20as%20the%20opposition%20Conservative%20Party%2C%20led%20by%20Pierre%20Poilievre%2C%20enjoys%20a%20commanding%20lead%20in%20public%20opinion%20polls.%20Poilievre%20has%20capitalised%20on%20economic%20frustrations%2C%20vowing%20to%20repeal%20Trudeau's%20carbon%20tax%20and%20address%20Canada's%20housing%20crisis.%20Some%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2F338canada.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epolls%3C%2Fa%3E%20show%20the%20Conservatives%20with%20a%20double-digit%20lead%20over%20the%20Liberals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrudeau's%20India%20Gambit%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETensions%20between%20New%20Delhi%20and%20Ottawa%20have%20been%20simmering%20since%20Trudeau's%20September%202023%20allegation%20of%20Indian%20involvement%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar.%20Nijjar%20was%20shot%20outside%20a%20Sikh%20temple%20in%20Canada.%20India%20dismissed%20the%20accusation%20as%20%26quot%3Babsurd.%26quot%3B%20Trudeau's%20claims%20that%20India%20sponsors%20criminal%20activities%20have%20drawn%20sharp%20criticism%20both%20domestically%20and%20internationally.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20subsequent%20fallout%2C%20India%20expelled%20six%20Canadian%20diplomats%20and%20recalled%20its%20envoy%20to%20Ottawa%20after%20Canada%20attempted%20to%20question%20Indian%20officials%20as%20%26quot%3Bpersons%20of%20interest%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20Nijjar%20case.%20Pro-Khalistan%20activities%20in%20Canada%2C%20including%20an%20attack%20on%20a%20Hindu%20temple%20near%20Toronto%2C%20further%20inflamed%20relations%20between%20the%20two%20nations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20consistently%20rejected%20any%20link%20to%20the%20murder%20of%20Nijjar%2C%20a%20designated%20terrorist%20by%20the%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20(NIA)%2C%20and%20accused%20Trudeau's%20administration%20of%20pandering%20to%20Khalistani%20sympathisers%20for%20political%20gain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20multiple%20exchanges%2C%20including%20meetings%20at%20international%20forums%20like%20the%20G20%20Summit%2C%20Canada%20has%20failed%20to%20provide%20any%20conclusive%20evidence%20linking%20India%20to%20the%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECritics%20argue%20that%20these%20allegations%20are%20an%20attempt%20to%20appeal%20to%20a%20segment%20of%20the%20Khalistani%20Sikh%20vote%20base%20in%20Canada%2C%20a%20move%20that%20some%20perceive%20as%20politically%20motivated.%20However%2C%20this%20strategy%20appears%20to%20h