%20unclear.%20Kyiv%20initially%20launched%20a%20surprise%20counteroffensive%20into%20Kursk%20in%20August%2C%20where%20it%20took%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkursk-battle-ukraine-russia-war-strategy-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eestimated%20480%20square%20miles%20of%20Russian%20land%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20has%20been%20slowly%20pushed%20back%20since.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20has%20stayed%20mostly%20silent%20on%20the%20matter.%20But%20Andriy%20Kovalenko%2C%20head%20of%20the%20Center%20for%20Countering%20Disinformation%20run%20by%20Ukraine's%20national%20security%20and%20defense%20council%2C%20alluded%20to%20an%20assault%20on%20Sunday%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fakovalenko1989%2F8542%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eposting%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Russian%20troops%20in%20Kursk%20%26quot%3Bwere%20attacked%20from%20several%20directions%20and%20it%20came%20as%20a%20surprise%20to%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAndriy%20Yermak%2C%20chief%20of%20staff%20for%20Ukraine's%20president%2C%20also%20hinted%20at%20an%20attack%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fermaka2022%2F5672%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewriting%20on%20his%20Telegram%20channel%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Russia%20was%20%26quot%3Bgetting%20what%20it%20deserves%26quot%3B%20in%20Kursk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Russia%20has%20outright%20declared%20that%20Ukraine%20had%20attacked%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20January%205%2C%20at%20about%2009%3A00%20Moscow%20time%2C%20in%20order%20to%20stop%20the%20advance%20of%20Russian%20troops%20in%20the%20Kursk%20direction%2C%20the%20enemy%20launched%20a%20counterattack%20with%20an%20assault%20group%20consisting%20of%20two%20tanks%2C%20a%20barrier%20vehicle%2C%20and%2012%20combat%20armored%20vehicles%20with%20troops%20in%20the%20direction%20of%20the%20Berdin%20farm%2C%26quot%3B%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftass.ru%2Farmiya-i-opk%2F22824877%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C