20for%20multiple%20respiratory%20viral%20pathogens%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20emphasized%20that%20HMPV%20is%20already%20in%20circulation%20globally%2C%20including%20in%20India%2C%20and%20cases%20of%20respiratory%20illnesses%20associated%20with%20HMPV%20have%20been%20reported%20in%20various%20countries.%20Furthermore%2C%20based%20on%20current%20data%20from%20ICMR%20and%20the%20Integrated%20Disease%20Surveillance%20Programme%20(IDSP)%20network%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20unusual%20surge%20in%20Influenza-Like%20Illness%20(ILI)%20or%20Severe%20Acute%20Respiratory%20Illness%20(SARI)%20cases%20in%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ICMR%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20noted%20that%20while%20the%20Union%20Health%20Ministry%20is%20monitoring%20the%20situation%20through%20all%20available%20surveillance%20channels%2C%20ICMR%20will%20continue%20to%20track%20trends%20in%20HMPV%20circulation%20throughout%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Ftr0qgloo_icmr_625x300_06_January_25.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20Centre%20had%20announced%20that%20it%20is%20monitoring%20the%20HMPV%20and%20other%20respiratory%20viruses%20following%20the%20surge%20of%20cases%20in%20China.%20A%20Joint%20Monitoring%20Group%20(JMG)%20was%20held%20by%20representatives%20from%20the%20World%20Health%20Organisation%20(WHO)%2C%20National%20Centre%20for%20Disease%20Control%20(NCDC)%2C%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Medical%20Research%20(ICMR)%2C%20and%20other%20health%20organisations%2C%20to%20evaluate%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Karnataka%20and%20Maharashtra%20governments%20have%20issued%20guidelines%20for%20citizens.%20Kerala%20Health%20Minister%20Veena%20George%20also%20advised%20the%20elderly%20and%20pregnant%20women%20to%20wear%20masks%2C%20adding%20there%20is%20no%20need%20to%20panic%20as%20of%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20HMPV%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHMPV%2C%20first%20discovered%20in%202001%2C%20is%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Pneumoviridae%20family%20along%20with%20the%20Respiratory%20syncytial%20virus%20(RSV).%20The%20symptoms%20commonly%20associated%20with%20the%20virus%20include%20cough%2C%20fever%2C%20nasal%20congestion%2C%20and%20shortness%20of%20breath.%20HMPV%20can%20occasionally%20trigger%20pneumonia%20or%20chronic%20respiratory%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20can%20spread%20from%20an%20infected%20individual%20to%20others%20through%20coughing%2C%20sneezing%20or%20personal%20contact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYoung%20children%2C%20older%20adults%20and%20those%20with%20weakened%20immune%20systems%20are%20at%20a%20higher%20risk%20of%20developing%20severe%20illness%20due%20to%20HMPV.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736148900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-12%2F1c0t3qog_covid-india_625x300_27_December_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhmpv-already-in-circulation-including-in-india-top-medical-body-icmr-7410226%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20the%20rising%20Human%20Metapneumovirus%20(HMPV)%20scare%2C%20the%20top%20medical%20body%20-%20the%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Medical%20Research%20or%20ICMR%20-%20on%20Monday%20alerted%20that%20the%20virus%20is%20already%20in%20%26quot%3Bcirculation%26quot%3B%20globally%2C%20including%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhmpv-already-in-circulation-including-in-india-top-medical-body-icmr-7410226%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Health%20Ministry%20Confirms%20Two%20HMPV%20Cases%20In%20India%3B%20Know%20Symptoms%20And%20Prevention%20Tips%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20surge%20in%20China%2C%20two%20cases%20of%20human%20metapneumovirus%20(HMPV)%20have%20been%20detected%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20India.%20An%20eight-month-old%20who%20is%20recovering%20in%20the%20hospital%20and%20a%20three-month-old%20who%20has%20been%20discharged%20are%20the%20first%20reported%20cases%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F3-month-old-and-8-month-old-babies-diagnosed-with-hmpv-in-bengaluru-7409670%5C%22%3EHMPV%20in%20India.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Currently%2C%20China%20is%20witnessing%20an%20HMPV%20outbreak.%20According%20to%20social%20media%20posts%2C%20multiple%20viruses%2C%20including%20influenza%20A%2C%20HMPV%2C%20Mycoplasma%20pneumoniae%2C%20and%20COVID-19%2C%20are%20circulating%20in%20China.%20Several%20videos%20and%20posts%20on%20social%20media%20suggest%20that%20hospitals%20are%20overwhelmed%20with%20individuals%20struggling%20with%20respiratory%20illnesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHMPV%2C%20first%20identified%20in%202001%2C%20is%20a%20respiratory%20infection%20that%20causes%20flu-like%20symptoms.%20It%20can%20affect%20people%20of%20all%20ages%2C%20however%2C%20young%20children(below%205%20years)%2C%20older%20adults%20and%20those%20with%20weakened%20immune%20systems%20are%20at%20a%20higher%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3ESymptoms%20of%20HMPV%3A%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECough%2C%20fever%2C%20nasal%20congestion%2C%20shortness%20of%20breath%2C%20and%20sore%20throat%20are%20a%20few%20symptoms%20of%20HMPV.%20These%20symptoms%20usually%20show%20up%20three%20to%20six%20days%20after%20you%20have%20been%20exposed%20to%20the%20virus.%20Severe%20illness%20due%20to%20HMPV%20may%20require%20hospitalisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3EHow%20is%20HMPV%20transmitted%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fhealth%2Fnew-virus-outbreak-in-china-what-is-hmpv-know-symptoms-prevention-tips-and-more-7389823%5C%22%3EHMPV%3C%2Fa%3E%20spreads%20through%20direct%20contact%20with%20someone%20who%20has%20it.%20Touching%20contaminated%20surfaces%2C%20coughing%2C%20snee