-octopus-with-broken-arms-week-1-2025-1236266639%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BEvery%20Law%20Broken%26quot%3B%3A%20BJP%20Gets%20Fresh%20'Sheesh%20Mahal'%20Ammo%20After%20Centre%20Audit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20report%20by%20the%20Comptroller%20and%20Auditor%20General%20of%20India%20(CAG)%20on%20the%20expenses%20made%20in%20renovating%20the%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister's%20residence%20has%20given%20the%20BJP%20fresh%20ammo%20to%20attack%20the%20ruling%20AAP%20and%20its%20leader%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20as%20the%20national%20capital%20preps%20for%20the%20Assembly%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CAG%20probe%2C%20according%20to%20news%20reports%2C%20found%20that%20the%20preliminary%20estimate%20for%20the%20renovation%20was%20Rs%207.91%20crore.%20This%20went%20up%20to%208.62%20crore%20when%20work%20was%20awarded%20in%202020.%20But%20by%20the%20time%20the%20Public%20Works%20Department%20completed%20the%20job%20in%202022%2C%20the%20cost%20had%20jumped%20to%20Rs%2033.66%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20in%20The%20Indian%20Express%2C%20former%20CAG%20Girish%20Chandra%20Murmu%20signed%20off%20on%20this%20report%20just%20a%20week%20before%20he%20left%20office%20in%20November.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20media%20today%2C%20Delhi%20BJP%20chief%20Virendraa%20Sachdeva%20said%20the%20sum%20of%20Rs%2033.66%20crore%20was%20%26quot%3Bjust%20a%20figure%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20actual%20renovation%20cost%20was%20much%20higher.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20want%20to%20estimate%20the%20actual%20cost%20of%20this%20bungalow%2C%20it%20will%20require%20examining%20the%20accounts%20of%20various%20departments%20and%20adding%20the%20inventory%20prepared%20by%20PWD%20on%20October%2011%2C%202024.%20We%20will%20then%20find%20that%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20'Sheesh%20Mahal'%20was%20illegally%20constructed%20and%20decorated%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20approximately%20Rs%2075%20to%2080%20crore%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20used%20the%20'Sheesh%20Mahal'%20expression%20to%20refer%20to%20the%20renovated%20Chief%20Minister's%20bungalow.%20The%20Opposition%20party%20has%20accused%20AAP%20and%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20of%20large-scale%20corruption%20in%20the%20renovation%20exercise%2C%20a%20charge%20AAP%20has%20trashed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CAG%20report%20has%20flagged%20%26quot%3Bdoubtful%26quot%3B%20selection%20of%20consultants%2C%20frequent%20revision%20of%20estimates%20and%20going%20beyond%20approvals%20to%20include%20items%20of%20higher%20specifications.%20The%20report%20also%20raised%20questions%20on%20the%20PWD's%20tender%20process%20to%20identify%20contractors%20for%20the%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20first%20clear%20fact%20from%20the%20CAG%20report%20about%20the%20%26quot%3BSheesh%20Mahal%26quot%3B%20is%20that%20under%20the%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20government%2C%20the%20PWD%20did%20not%20act%20as%20a%20government%20agency%20but%20as%20a%20personal%20institution%20for%20Chief%20Minister%20Kejriwal%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Delhi%20BJP%20chief%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20important%20to%20note%20that%20the%20way%20PWD%20officials%20broke%20every%20rule%20and%20law%20to%20build%20this%20'Sheesh%20Mahal'%20makes%20it%20clear%20that%20this%20is%20a%20case%20of%20corruption%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Bgive%20and%20take%26quot%3B%20situation%20-%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20the%20concerned%20ministers%20must%20have%20also%20turned%20a%20blind%20eye%20to%20the%20many%20corrupt%20activities%20of%20the%20officials%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sachdeva%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20also%20said%20PWD%20declared%20it%20an%20emergency%20project%20and%20issued%20the%20work%20order%20on%20September%201%2C%202020.%20%26quot%3BThis%20was%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20when%20people%20were%20struggling%20and%20jobs%20were%20suspended%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BJP%20said%2C%20questioning%20the%20urgency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20referred%20to%20the%20CAG%20report%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20will%20be%20shocked%20to%20know%20that%20when%20Delhi%20residents%20were%20fighting%20Covid%2C%20wandering%20in%20search%20of%20oxygen%20and%20medicines%2C%20their%20(AAP)%20focus%20was%20on%20the%20building%20Sheesh%20Mahal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHitting%20back%20at%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20said%20the%20man%20who%20lives%20in%20a%20house%20worth%20Rs%202%2C700%20crore%2C%20travels%20on%20an%20Rs%208%2C400%20crore%20plane%20and%20wears%20a%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20suit%20must%20not%20talk%20about%20Sheesh%20Mahal.%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20has%20vacated%20the%20bungalow%20after%20he%20quit%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20post%2C%20saying%20that%20he%20will%20return%20to%20the%20top%20job%20only%20after%20the%20%26quot%3Bpeople's%20verdict%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20Assembly%20election%20due%20in%20February.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736148540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fr1crnvpg_arvind-kejriwal-delhi-home-sheesh-mahal_625x300_27_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-delhi-election-every-law-broken-bjp-gets-fresh-sheesh-mahal-ammo-after-centre-audit-7410174%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20report%20by%20the%20Comptroller%20and%20Auditor%20General%20of%20India%20(CAG)%20on%20the%20expenses%20made%20in%20renovating%20the%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister's%20residence%20has%20given%20the%20BJP%20fresh%20ammo%20to%20attack%20the%20ruling%20AAP%20and%20its%20leader%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20as%20the%20capital%20preps%20for%20polls%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-delhi-election-every-law-broken-bjp-gets-fresh-sheesh-mahal-ammo-after-centre-audit-7410174%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22With%20new%