2C%20AWIAL%20Misses%20Out%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%202025%20Golden%20Globes%20Awards%20were%20held%20at%20the%20Beverly%20Hilton%20in%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20US%2C%20on%20January%205%2C%202025%2C%20with%20Hollywood%20A-listers%20in%20attendance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20had%20its%20hopes%20pinned%20on%20the%20Cannes-winning%20film%20%3Cem%3EAll%20We%20Imagine%20As%20Light%20%3C%2Fem%3E(directed%20by%20Payal%20Kapadia)%2C%20which%20secured%20nominations%20in%20two%20categories%20-%20Best%20Non-English%20Language%20Motion%20Picture%20and%20Best%20Director.%20However%2C%20%3Cem%3EAll%20We%20Imagine%20As%20Light%3C%2Fem%3E%20failed%20to%20take%20home%20any%20award.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPayal%20Kapadia%2C%20dressed%20in%20a%20black%20ensemble%2C%20was%20present%20at%20the%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20of%20the%20big%20wins%20this%20season%2C%20%3Cem%3EEmilia%20Perez%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Brutalist%20%3C%2Fem%3Edominated%20the%20chart.%20In%20the%20Television%20category%2C%20%3Cem%3EShogun%20%3C%2Fem%3Eretained%20its%20dominance%20with%20four%20wins.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEmilia%20Perez%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20was%20leading%20the%20nominations%20with%2010%20nods%2C%20ended%20up%20with%20four%20awards.%20It%20won%20awards%20for%20the%20Best%20Motion%20Picture%20(Musical%2FComedy)%2C%20Best%20Non-English%20Language%20Film%20and%20Best%20Original%20Song.%20Zoe%20Saldana%20won%20the%20Best%20Supporting%20Actor%20award%20for%20%3Cem%3EEmilia%20Perez%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20acceptance%20speech%2C%20Zoe%20said%20with%20tears%20in%20her%20eyes%2C%20%26quot%3BMy%20heart%20is%20full%20of%20gratitude.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20hailed%20the%20%26quot%3Bstrength%2C%20complexity%20and%20undeniable%20talent%26quot%3B%20of%20co-stars%20Selena%20Gomez%20and%20Karla%20Sofia%20Gascon%2C%20as%20well%20as%20director%20Jacques%20Audiard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Brutalist%3C%2Fem%3E%20won%20the%20awards%20for%20the%20