3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBoth%20cases%20were%20identified%20through%20routine%20surveillance%20for%20multiple%20respiratory%20viral%20pathogens%2C%20as%20part%20of%20ICMR's%20ongoing%20efforts%20to%20monitor%20respiratory%20illnesses%20across%20the%20country.%20HMPV%20is%20already%20in%20circulation%20globally%2C%20including%20in%20India%2C%20and%20cases%20of%20respiratory%20illnesses%20associated%20with%20HMPV%20have%20been%20reported%20in%20various%20countries%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Centre%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Health%20Ministry%20has%20convened%20a%20meeting%20on%20HMPV%20preparedness%20today.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHMPV%20is%20a%20respiratory%20virus%20that%20often%20causes%20mild%20symptoms%20resembling%20a%20cold%20but%20can%20lead%20to%20other%20complications%2C%20particularly%20in%20infants%2C%20the%20elderly%2C%20and%20those%20with%20weakened%20immune%20systems.%20The%20virus%20can%20occasionally%20trigger%20pneumonia%20or%20exacerbate%20chronic%20respiratory%20conditions.%20Cases%20typically%20rise%20during%20the%20winter%20and%20early%20spring.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20announced%20on%20Sunday%20that%20it%20is%20monitoring%20HMPV%20and%20other%20respiratory%20viruses%2C%20especially%20following%20recent%20reports%20of%20increased%20respiratory%20illnesses%20in%20China.%20A%20Joint%20Monitoring%20Group%20(JMG)%20convened%20on%20January%204%20to%20evaluate%20the%20situation%2C%20with%20representatives%20from%20the%20World%20Health%20Organisation%20(WHO)%2C%20National%20Centre%20for%20Disease%20Control%20(NCDC)%2C%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Medical%20Research%20(ICMR)%2C%20and%20other%20health%20organisations%20participating.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERespiratory%20illnesses%20in%20China%20align%20with%20seasonal%20variations%20caused%20by%20viruses%20such%20as%20influenza%2C%20RSV%2C%20and%20HMPV.%20Current%20surveillance%20data%20from%20India%20does%20not%20indicate%20any%20unusual%20surge%20in%20respiratory%20infections%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Health%20and%20Family%20Welfare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20precaution%2C%20the%20Centre%20has%20increased%20laboratory%20capacity%20for%20HMPV%20testing.%20The%20ICMR%20will%20monitor%20HMPV%20trends%20throughout%20the%20year%2C%20alongside%20other%20respiratory%20illnesses%20such%20as%20influenza-like%20illness%20(ILI)%20and%20severe%20acute%20respiratory%20infections%20(SARI).%20A%20robust%20network%20of%20surveillance%20systems%2C%20including%20those%20operated%20by%20ICMR%20and%20the%20Integrated%20Disease%20Surveillance%20Programme%20(IDSP)%2C%20continues%20to%20track%20respiratory%20infections%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHospitals%20have%20been%20advised%20to%20strengthen%20isolation%20protocols%20for%20suspected%20cases%2C%20ensure%20the%20availability%20of%20essential%20medicines%2C%20and%20promptly%20report%20ILI%20and%20SARI%20cases%20through%20the%20Integrated%20Health%20Information%20Platform%20(IHIP).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736145660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fb9klb12_hospital-generic-_625x300_15_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F3-month-old-and-8-month-old-babies-diagnosed-with-hmpv-in-bengaluru-7409670%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%223-Month-Old%20And%208-MTwo%20cases%20of%20Human%20Metapneumovirus%20(HMPV)%20were%20reported%20in%20Bengaluru%20today%20-%20a%203-month-old%20baby%20who%20has%20been%20discharged%20and%20an%208-month-old%20who%20is%20recovering%20at%20a%20hospital%20in%20the%20Karnataka%20capital.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A22%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F3-month-old-and-8-month-old-babies-diagnosed-with-hmpv-in-bengaluru-7409670%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ira-Nupur%20groove%20on%20Junaid's%20Loveyapa%20title%20track%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736145225