2C%20former%20Google%20CEO%20Eric%20Schmidt%2C%20and%20LinkedIn%20cofounder%20Reid%20Hoffman%2C%20have%20all%20highlighted%20the%20importance%20of%20fostering%20a%20culture%20of%20disagreement%20from%20the%20top.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%202016%20letter%20to%20shareholders%2C%20Bezos%20wrote%20about%20how%20employees%20should%20embrace%20his%20%26quot%3Bdisagree%20and%20commit%26quot%3B%20strategy%2C%20which%20is%20a%20way%20to%20say%3A%20%26quot%3BLook%2C%20I%20know%20we%20disagree%20on%20this%20but%20will%20you%20gamble%20with%20me%20on%20it%3F%20Disagree%20and%20commit%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20isn't%20one%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20Bezos%20added.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20the%20boss%2C%20you%20should%20do%20this%20too.%20I%20disagree%20and%20commit%20all%20the%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJoseph%20Grenny%2C%20a%20corporate%20trainer%20and%20the%20coauthor%20of%20the%20workplace%20strategy%20book%20%26quot%3BCrucial%20Conversations%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20staying%20silent%20can%20carry%20its%20own%20pitfalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%202016%20interview%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhbr.org%2F2016%2F03%2Fhow-to-disagree-with-someone-more-powerful-than-you%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHarvard%20Business%20Review%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20suggested%20considering%20%26quot%3Bthe%20risks%20of%20not%20speaking%20up%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20which%20could%20be%20the%20project%20falling%20apart%20or%20losing%20the%20team's%20trust%20%E2%80%94%20and%20weighing%20those%20against%20the%20consequences%20of%20saying%20something.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20way%20to%20do%20it%20is%20to%20ask%20your%20manager%20for%20permission%20to%20disagree%2C%20Grenny%20said%2C%20by%20saying%20something%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20know%20we%20seem%20to%20be%20moving%20toward%20a%20first-quarter%20commitment%20here.%20I%20have%20reasons%20to%20think%20that%20won't%20work.%20I'd%20like%20to%20lay%20out%20my%20reasoning.%20Would%20that%20be%20OK%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESabina%20Nawaz%2C%20a%20CEO%20coach%20who%20was%20a%20senior%20director%20of%20human%20resources%20at%20Microsoft%20for%2015%20years%2C%20wrote%20in%20a%202023%20LinkedIn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fpulse%2Fhow-disagree-work-without-harming-relationships-sabina-nawaz%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epost%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20avoiding%20disagreement%20is%20more%20damaging%20to%20relationships%20than%20speaking%20up.%20She%20recommended%20finding%20allies%20for%20meetings%20and%20asking%20what%20others%20think.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20co-workers%20realize%20you%20let%20them%20proceed%20with%20a%20faulty%20plan%2C%20or%20waited%20until%20the%20last%20minute%20to%20raise%20objections%2C%20they're%20likely%20to%20lose%20trust%20in%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20Nawaz%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-openai-leadership-style-disagreement-positive-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736143151000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d60a65a610a9069d5ad69e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-openai-leadership-style-disagreement-positive-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Other%20tech%20leaders%20swear%20by%20a%20culture%20of%20disagreement%20from%20the%20top.%20One%20of%20Jeff%20Bezos's%20leadership%20principles%20is%20%26quot%3Bdisagree%20and%20commit.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22shubhangigoel%40insider.com%20(Shubhangi%20Goel)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A86%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-openai-leadership-style-disagreement-positive-2025-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22High%20Drama%20In%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Assembly%20Amid%20Protests%20On%20Anna%20University%20Rape%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETamil%20Nadu%20Assembly's%20first%20session%20of%20the%20year%20got%20off%20to%20a%20stormy%20start%20on%20Monday%20as%20the%20Opposition%20AIADMK%20and%20BJP%20MLAs%20protested%20and%20raised%20slogans%20against%20the%20Anna%20University%20sexual%20assault%20case.%20Several%20leaders%2C%20including%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20Edappadi%20K%20Palaniswami%20-%20who%20led%20the%20protest%20-%20also%20held%20placards%20in%20the%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Assembly%20Speaker%20M%20Appavu%20asked%20the%20protesting%20MLAs%20to%20stop%20the%20sloganeering.%20However%2C%20as%20they%20did%20not%20stop%2C%20the%20Speaker%20ordered%20marshalls%20to%20evacuate%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20this%2C%20Pattali%20Makkal%20Katchi%20(PMK)%20and%20other%20BJP%20leaders%20also%20walked%20out%20of%20the%20Assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20BJP%20MLA%2C%20Vanathi%20Srinivasan%2C%20they%20do%20not%20have%20any%20faith%20in%20the%20government's%20investigation%20into%20the%20sexual%20assault%20case.%20%26quot%3BWe%20suspect%20someone%20is%20being%20safeguarded...Opposition%20is%20not%20politicising%20the%20issue.%20We%20are%20raising%20women's%20safety%20issues%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20DMK%20government%20has%20been%20facing%20challenges%20as%20its%20allied%20party%2C%20the%20VCK%2C%20also%20submitted%20a%20notice%20to%20the%20Speaker%20to%20discuss%20the%20issues%20surrounding%20the%20Anna%20University%20sexual%20assault%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20took%20place%20on%20December%2023%2C%20when%20a%2019-year-old%20engineering%20student%20was%20allegedly%20sexually%20assaulted%20on%20the%20Anna%20University%20campus.%20The%20victim%2C%20in%20her%20complaint%2C%20said%20that%20the%20assailant%20had%20attacked%20her%20and%20her%20male%20friend%2C%20brutally%20assaulting%20the%20latter%20before%20dragging%20her%20into%20nearby%20shrubs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20person%2C%20Gnanasekaran%20-%20%C2%A0a%20roadside%20biryani%20vendor%20-%20was%20arrested%20shortly%20after%20the%20complaint%20was%20filed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EAIADMK%20students'%20wing%20members%20detained%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAIADMK%20Students'%20wing%20members%20held%20a%20protest%20outside%20Anna%20University%20on%20Monday%20morning.%20They%20distributed%20black%20bands%20to%20the%20students%20and%20public%20as%20a%20mark%20of%20support%20to%20the%20victim%20and%20to%20garner%20the%20attention%20of%20the%20state%20government%20to%20arrest%20the%20real%20accused%2C%20an%20AIADMK%20member%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20students%2C%20however%2C%20were%20detained%20as%20they%20were%20denied%20permission%20to%20hold%20the%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20would%20be%20released%20later%20in%20the%20day%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnother%20high%20drama%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20assembly%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20high%20drama%20followed%20in%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Assembly%20as%20Governor%20TN%20Ravi%20walked%20out%20of%20the%20inaugural%20session%20of%20the%20House%2C%20accusing%20DMK%20of%20disrespecting%20the%20Constitution%20by%20refusing%20to%20sing%20the%20National%20Anthem%20before%20the%20session%20convened.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Constitution%20of%20Bharat%20and%20the%20National%20Anthem%20were%20once%20again%20insulted%20in%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Assembly%20today.%20Respecting%20the%20National%20Anthem%20is%20among%20the%20first%20Fundamental%20Duty%20as%20enshrined%20in%20our%20Constitution.%20It%20is%20sung%20in%20all%20the%20state%20legislatures%20at%20the%20beginning%20and%20the%20end%20of%20Governor's%20address.%20Today%20on%20the%20arrival%20of%20the%20Governor%20to%20the%20House%20only%20Tamil%20Thaai%20Vaazhthu%20was%20sung%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20added%20that%20while%20the%20Governor%20%26quot%3Brespectfully%20reminded%26quot%3B%20the%20House%20to%20play%20the%20national%20anthem%2C%20they%20%26quot%3Bcussedly%20refused%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20grave%20concern.%20Not%20to%20be%20a%20party%20to%20such%20brazen%20disrespect%20to%20the%20Constitution%20and%20the%20National%20Anthem%2C%20Governor%20in%20deep%20anguish%20left%20the%20House%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20post%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Assembly%20reportedly%20has%20a%20tradition%20of%20beginning%20and%20ending%20the%20session%20with%20the%20national%20anthem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Governor%20also%20did%20not%20deliver%20the%20customary%20address%20to%20the%20Assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20the%20Governor%20has%20walked%20out%20of%20the%20Assembly%20and%20refused%20to%20deliver%20the%20address.%20In%202023%2C%20dramatic%20scenes%20played%20out%20in%20the%20Assembly%20when%20TN%20Ravi%20skipped%20parts%20of%20the%20official%20speech%20prepared%20by%20the%20DMK.%20He%20did%20not%20mention%20parts%20of%20the%20address%20that%20mentioned%20leaders%20such%20as%20Periyar%2C%20BR%20Ambedkar%2C%20K%20Kamaraj%2C%20CN%20Annadurai%2C%20and%20K%20Karunanidhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736143080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fasgf4m4o_anna-uni_625x300_06_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhigh-drama-in-tamil-nadu-assembly-amid-opposition-aiadmk-bjp-protests-on-anna-university-rape-case-7409589%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tamil%20Nadu%20Assembly's%20first%20session%20of%20the%20year%20got%20off%20to%20a%20stormy%20start%20on%20Monday%20as%20the%20Opposition%20AIADMK%20and%20BJP%20MLAs%20protested%20and%20raised%20slogans%20against%20the%20Anna%20University%20sexual%20assault%20case.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhigh-drama-in-tamil-nadu-assembly-amid-opposition-aiadmk-bjp-protests-on-anna-university-rape-case-7409589%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Antariksha%20Jugalbandi'%3A%20How%20India%20Aims%20Historic%20Docking%20Experiment%20In%20Space%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20will%20conduct%20a%20docking%20experiment%20in%20space%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20This%20can%20also%20be%20referred%20to%20as%20%26quot%3BISRO's%20Ballet%20in%20Space%26quot%3B%2C%20or%20an%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Eantariksha%20jugalbandi%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B.%20Two%20small%2C%20functioning%20homegrown%20satellites%20will%20be%20mated%20together%20in%20space.%20The%20complexities%20of%20this%20hugely%20significant%20mission%20are%20many.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%20are%20some%20of%20the%20challenges%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20satellites%20in%20space%20are%20mated%20together%20to%20make%20one%20spacecraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20December%2030%2C%202024%2C%20India%20successfully%20launched%20the%20SpaDeX%20mission%20using%20the%20workhorse%20Polar%20Satellite%20Launch%20Vehicle%20(PSLV).%20The%20twin%20220-kg%20satellites%20were%20released%20in%20a%20precise%20470-km%20circular%20orbit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20the%20chaser%20and%20the%20target%20satellites%20-%20as%20they%20are%20called%20-%20have%20been%20stabilised%20in%20the%20same%20orbit%2C%20separated%20by%20a%2020-km%20difference.%20Both%20satellites%20are%20equipped%20with%20a%20suite%20of%20special%20homegrown%20ranging%20and%20tracking%20sensors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20satellites%20in%20orbit%20will%20be%20flying%20at%2028%2C800%20kmph%2C%20or%2010%20times%20the%20speed%20of%20a%20bullet.%20But%20since%20both%20travel%20together%2C%20they%20appear%20stationary%20to%20each%20other%20as%20the%20relative%20velocity%20is%20what%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20docking%20process%20begins%2C%20the%20satellites%20will%20be%20progressively%20brought%20closer.%20The%20chaser%20will%20approach%20the%20target%20with%20progressively%20reduced%20inter-satellite%20distances%20of%205%20km%2C%201.5%20km%2C%20500%20m%2C%20225%20m%2C%2015%20m%2C%20and%203%20m%2C%20ultimately%20leading%20to%20the%20precise%20docking%20of%20the%20two%20spacecraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20docking%20happens%2C%20the%20chaser%20will%20inch%20closer%20to%20the%20target%20at%20a%20speed%20of%2010%20mm%20per%20second.%20Then%20the%20special%20clasps%20will%20hold%20the%20satellites%20together%20in%20a%20tight%20embrace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20test%20if%20docking%20is%20successful%2C%20electrical%20power%20will%20be%20transferred%20from%20one%20satellite%20to%20the%20other.%20After%20docking%2C%20the%20satellites%20will%20be%20controlled%20as%20a%20single%20spacecraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20space-docking%20experiment%20is%20completed%2C%20the%20two%20satellites%20will%20be%20separated%20and%20then%20each%20will%20go%20on%20to%20do%20independent%20experiments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20system%2C%20developed%20indigenously%2C%20is%20named%20Bhartiya%20Docking%20System.%20India%20needs%20to%20master%20this%20docking%20technology%20for%20completing%20future%20missions%20such%20as%20Chandrayaan%204%20and%20to%20make%20the%20Bhartiya%20Antariksha%20Station%20and%20Gaganyaan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20such%20a%20complex%20process%20that%20only%20Russia%2C%20the%20US%2C%20and%20China%20have%20perfected%20it%20till%20now.%20No%20nation%20shares%20fine%20details%20of%20this%20challenging%20technology%2C%20hence%20the%20swadeshi%20effort.%20If%20successful%2C%20India%20will%20become%20a%20full-fledged%20space-faring%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736142840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F8bkemofo_isro-_625x300_06_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhow-india-isro-aims-historic-docking-experiment-in-space-antariksha-jugalbandi-7407361%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20will%20conduct%20a%20space-docking%20experiment%20in%2