iginID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fhmpv-india-first-case-bengaluru-baby-infection-private-hospital-125010600249_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22If%20the%20infection%20is%20confirmed%2C%20it%20would%20be%20the%20first%20reported%20case%20of%20HMPV%20in%20India%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fhmpv-india-first-case-bengaluru-baby-infection-private-hospital-125010600249_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk%2C%20Pakistani%20Grooming%20Gangs%3A%20World's%20Richest%20Man%20Sparks%20UK%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20world's%20richest%20man%2C%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20has%20sparked%20a%20political%20storm%20in%20the%20UK%20by%20launching%20a%20series%20of%20controversial%20posts%20targeting%20Prime%20Minister%20Keir%20Starmer%20and%20the%20Labour%20government.%20His%20comments%20have%20reopened%20discussions%20around%20the%20issue%20of%20child%20grooming%20gangs%2C%20sparking%20calls%20for%20fresh%20investigations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMusk's%20Allegations%20Against%20Starmer%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20New%20Year's%20Day%2C%20Musk%20accused%20Keir%20Starmer%20of%20failing%20to%20act%20decisively%20on%20grooming%20gang%20cases%20during%20his%20tenure%20as%20Director%20of%20Public%20Prosecutions%20(2008-2013).%20Musk%20claimed%20that%20Starmer%20allowed%20%26quot%3Brape%20gangs%26quot%3B%20to%20exploit%20vulnerable%20girls%20without%20facing%20justice%2C%20alleging%20that%20institutional%20failures%20were%20linked%20to%20Starmer's%20leadership%20of%20the%20Crown%20Prosecution%20Service%20(CPS).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20billionaire%20also%20criticised%20Jess%20Phillips%2C%20the%20safeguarding%20minister%20-%20a%20position%20under%20the%20UK%20Home%20Office%2C%20accusing%20her%20of%20covering%20up%20for%20Starmer%20by%20rejecting%20a%20call%20for%20a%20public%20inquiry%20into%20alleged%20grooming%20scandals%20in%20Oldham.%20Musk%20suggested%20that%20Phillips'%20decision%20was%20politically%20motivated%20to%20shield%20Starmer%2C%20claiming%20it%20represented%20a%20%26quot%3Bcover-up%26quot%3B%20of%20systemic%20failings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20series%20of%20posts%20on%20X%2C%20Musk%20demanded%20a%20new%20national%20public%20inquiry%20and%20called%20for%20the%20Labour%20government%20to%20face%20an%20immediate%20general%20election.%20He%20went%20so%20far%20as%20to%20accuse%20Phillips%20of%20being%20a%20%26quot%3Brape%20genocide%20apologist%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Labour%20government%20was%20quick%20to%20dismiss%20Musk's%20remarks%2C%20with%20Health%20Secretary%20Wes%20Streeting%20labelling%20them%20%26quot%3Bmisjudged%20and%20misinformed.%26quot%3B%20Starmer's%20defenders%20argue%20that%20as%20DPP%2C%20he%20introduced%20new%20guidelines%20in%202013%20to%20better%20address%20child%20sexual%20exploitation%20cases.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EGrooming%20Gang%20Scandals%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20grooming%20gang%20scandals%20have%20long%20been%20a%20flashpoint%20in%20UK%20politics.%20Investigations%20in%20towns%20such%20as%20Rotherham%2C%20Rochdale%2C%20and%20Telford%20revealed%20widespread%20child%20sexual%20exploitation%2C%20often%20perpetrated%20by%20men%20of%20predominantly%20Pakistani%20descent.%20Reports%20suggested%20systemic%20failings%20by%20local%20authorities%20and%20law%20enforcement%2C%20with%20officials%20accused%20of%20ignoring%20or%20downplaying%20abuse%20due%20to%20fears%20of%20being%20labelled%20racist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202022%20Oldham%20inquiry%20found%20serious%20safeguarding%20failures%20but%20did%20not%20uncover%20evidence%20of%20organised%20exploitation%20in%20council-run%20facilities.%20National%20inquiries%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Independent%20Inquiry%20into%20Child%20Sexual%20Abuse%20(IICSA)%2C%20have%20repeatedly%20identified%20gaps%20in%20the%20system%2C%20while%20successive%20governments%20have%20pledged%20reforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20failures%20have%20been%20seized%20upon%20by%20far-right%20figures%20like%20Tommy%20Robinson%20and%20Nigel%20Farage%20to%20stoke%20anti-immigrant%20sentiment.%20Musk's%20decision%20to%20amplify%20Robinson's%20views%20has%20led%20critics%20to%20accuse%20him%20of%20spreading%20disinformation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMusk%20vs%20Farage%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Tesla%20chief%20has%20aligned%20himself%20with%20far-right%20movements%20in%20Europe%20and%20expressed%20support%20for%20Britain's%20Reform%20UK%20party%2C%20led%20by%20Nigel%20Farage.%20Musk%20has%20also%20championed%20the%20cause%20of%20agitator%20Robinson%2C%20currently%20serving%20an%2018-month%20sentence%20for%20contempt%20of%20court%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20however%2C%20Musk%20appeared%20to%20distance%20himself%20from%20Nigel%20Farage%2C%20the%20leader%20of%20Britain's%20anti-immigration%20Reform%20UK%20party.%20Musk%2C%20who%20previously%20signalled%20potential%20support%20for%20Farage's%20party%2C%20declared%20on%20his%20X%20platform%20that%20%26quot%3BThe%20Reform%20Party%20needs%20a%20new%20leader.%20Farage%20doesn't%20have%20what%20it%20takes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20public%20rift%20comes%20days%20after%20Farage%20revealed%20he%20had%20been%20in%20talks%20with%20Musk%20regarding%20a%20possible%20significant%20financial%20donation%20to%20Reform%20UK.%20Farage's%20party%2C%20which%20split%20the%20conservative%20vote%20during%20the%20general%20election%20in%20July%202024%2C%20is%20seen%20as%20influential%20in%20Labour's%20return%20to%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk%20posted%20on%20X%20questioning%20why%20Robinson%20was%20in%20solitary%20confinement%2C%20claiming%20it%20was%20for%20%26quot%3Btelling%20the%20truth%26quot%3B%20about%20grooming%20gangs%2C%20a%20series%20of%20scandals%20involving%20the%20exploitation%20of%20young%20girls%20by%20predominantly%20S