%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20more%20puzzling%20force%20management%20choices%26quot%3B%20Kyiv%20has%20made%2C%20the%20analyst%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine's%202024%20strategy%20for%20solving%20a%20shortage%20of%20soldiers%20%E2%80%94%20its%20biggest%20challenge%20thus%20far%20%E2%80%94%20by%20forming%20new%20brigades%20instead%20of%20reinforcing%20old%20ones%20is%20performing%20poorly%2C%20said%20a%20top%20analyst%20on%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMichael%20Kofman%2C%20a%20senior%20fellow%20for%20the%20Russia%20and%20Eurasia%20Program%20at%20the%20Carnegie%20Endowment%20for%20International%20Peace%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FKofmanMichael%2Fstatus%2F1875568077255131632%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%20in%20a%20social%20media%20thread%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Saturday%20that%20Kyiv's%20decision%20was%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20more%20puzzling%20force%20management%20choices%26quot%3B%20it%20has%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BExpanding%20the%20force%20with%20new%20brigades%2C%20when%20men%20are%20desperately%20needed%20to%20replace%20losses%20among%20experienced%20formations%20deployed%20on%20the%20front%20lines%2C%20had%20visible%20tradeoffs%2C%26quot%3B%20Kofman%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20little%20experience%2C%20the%20new%20units%20have%20been%20%26quot%3Bgenerally%20combat%20ineffective%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E'%26quot%3BAs%20was%20seen%20in%202023%2C%20new%20formations%20perform%20poorly%20in%20offensive%20and%20defensive%20roles.%20Requiring%20considerable%20time%20to%20gain%20experience%2C%20cohesion%2C%20confidence%2C%20etc.%2C%26quot%3B%20Kofman%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20result%20is%20that%20the%20strategy%20has%20at%20least%20partially%20disintegrated%2C%20with%20battalions%20from%20the%20new%20brigades%20eventually%20sent%20to%20shore%20up%20losses%20in%20units%20that%20were%20already%20fighting%2C%20Kofman%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20leadership%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.economist.com%2Feurope%2F2024%2F05%2F10%2Fukraine-will-hold-if-it-gets-the-arms-it-needs-says-a-top-general%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%20in%20May%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it%20aimed%20to%20create%2010%20new%20brigades%2C%20each%20of%20which%20typically%20consists%20of%20several%20thousand%20men.%20In%20doing%20so%2C%20its%20leaders%20hoped%20to%20provide%20fresh%20units%20that%20could%20rotate%20into%20combat%20or%20fill%20gaps%20on%20the%20front%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20simply%20no%20other%20effective%20way%20to%20counteract%20the%20overwhelming%20enemy%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20Ukraine's%20armed%20forces%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pravda.com.ua%2Fnews%2F2024%2F11%2F6%2F7483191%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%20in%20November%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BAfter%20all%2C%20today%20we%20have%20a%201%2C300%20km-long%20front%20with%20active%20combat%20clashes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20elements%20of%20these%20brigades%20were%20aided%20by%20training%20from%20Western%20forces%2C%20such%20as%20the%20155th%20Mechanized%20Brigade.%20About%20half%20of%20its%20recruits%20drilled%20in%20France.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-investigate-155th-mechanized-brigade-france-anne-kyiv-desertion-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E155th's%20debut%20late%20last%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%20created%20a%20crisis%20for%20Ukraine%20as%20reports%20emerged%20that%20it%20suffered%20from%20high%20rates%20of%20desertion%20and%20was%20being%20picked%20apart%20to%20siphon%20resources%20to%20other%20brigades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELocal%20journalist%20Yuriy%20Butusov%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-investigate-155th-mechanized-brigade-france-anne-kyiv-desertion-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20just%20before%20the%20New%20Year%20that%20the%20new%20brigade%2C%20often%20finding%20itself%20whittled%20down%2C%20had%20to%20juggle%20specialists%20such%20as%20drone%20jamming%20operators%20into%20infantry%20roles.%20The%20backlash%20to%20the%20news%20was%20severe%2C%20with%20Ukrainian%20figures%20voicing%20questions%20about%20the%20new%20strategy%20as%20a%20whole.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPerhaps%20it's%20sheer%20idiocy%20to%20create%20new%20brigades%20and%20equip%20them%20with%20new%20technology%20while%20existing%20ones%20are%20undermanned%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FBohdanKrotevych%2Fstatus%2F1874489196263428544%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%20Lt.%20Col.%20Bohdan%20Krotevych%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20serves%20as%20chief%20of%20staff%20in%20the%20Azov%20Brigade.%20The%20155th%20is%20supplied%20with%20dozens%20of%20French-made%20armored%20vehicles%2C%20howitzers%2C%20and%20personnel%20carriers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKofman%20wrote%20that%20the%20155th's%20scandal%20was%20%26quot%3Bjust%20the%20most%20egregious%20case%26quot%3B%20of%20Ukraine's%20force%20management%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDivvying%20up%20new%20units%20has%20led%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bsteady%20fragmentation%20of%20the%20defensive%20effort%20and%20loss%20of%20cohesion%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20patchwork%20groupings%20of%20forces%20must%20hold%20the%20front%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20has%2C%20over%20the%20last%20year%2C%20faced%20a%20slow%20but%20persistent%20Russian%20assault%20in%20the%20eastern%20regions%20of%20the%20Donbas%2C%20where%20Moscow%20has%20been%20throwing%20a%20steady%20supply%20of%20men%20and%20equipment%20at%20Kyiv's%20outnumbered%20and%20exhausted%20defensive%20lines.%20Russia's%20gains%20have%20been%20incremental%20and%20its%20reported%20losses%20are%20staggering%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-lost-over-420000-troops-1600-square-miles-2024-isw-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebut%20it%20is%20advancing%20nonetheless.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C