e%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20build%20a%20factory%20%E2%80%94%20build%20a%20lot%20of%20them%20%E2%80%94%20and%20you%20have%20to%20get%20regulatory%20approval.%20And%20that%20will%20take%2C%20you%20know%2C%20years%20altogether%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOklo%2C%20another%20Altman-backed%20nuclear%20power%20company%2C%20has%20yet%20to%20receive%20approval%20from%20the%20Nuclear%20Regulatory%20Commission%20after%20its%20previous%20application%20was%20denied%20in%202022%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftechcrunch.com%2F2024%2F12%2F18%2Fsam-altman-backed-nuclear-startup-oklo-lands-massive-data-center-power-deal-with-caveats%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETech%20Crunch%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20siding%20with%20Trump%20on%20a%20looser%20approach%20to%20regulation%20and%20infrastructure%20development%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAltman%20also%20hedged%20his%20prior%20support%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchips-act-funding-biden-administration-trump-tariffs-repeal-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECHIPS%20Act%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20multibillion-dollar%20manufacturing%20incentive%20for%20semiconductor%20production%20pushed%20forward%20by%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20CHIPS%20Act%20was%20better%20than%20doing%20nothing%20but%20not%20the%20thing%20that%20we%20should%20have%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20Altman%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20think%20there's%20a%20real%20opportunity%20to%20do%20something%20much%20better%20as%20a%20follow-on.%20I%20don't%20think%20the%20CHIPS%20Act%20has%20been%20as%20effective%20as%20any%20of%20us%20hoped.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20OpenAI%20chief%20reportedly%20wants%20to%20raise%20trillions%20of%20dollars%20to%20address%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-openai-raise-trillions-supercharge-chip-production-report-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5